graph TD
    A[Application Starts] --> B{Detect Platform}
    B -->|macOS| C[Query NSAppearance]
    B -->|Windows| D[Query DWM]
    B -->|Linux| E[Query GTK]

    C --> F[Read Accent Color<br/>NSColor.controlAccentColor]
    D --> G[Read Accent Color<br/>DwmGetColorizationColor]
    E --> H[Read Theme Name<br/>gtk-theme-name]

    F --> I{Dark Mode?}
    G --> J{Dark Mode?}
    H --> K{Dark Mode?}

    I -->|Yes| L[Build Dark Theme<br/>with System Accent]
    I -->|No| M[Build Light Theme<br/>with System Accent]
    J -->|Yes| N[Build Dark Theme<br/>with System Accent]
    J -->|No| O[Build Light Theme<br/>with System Accent]
    K -->|Yes| P[Build Dark Theme<br/>with System Accent]
    K -->|No| Q[Build Light Theme<br/>with System Accent]

    L --> R[Apply Theme to UI]
    M --> R
    N --> R
    O --> R
    P --> R
    Q --> R

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style R fill:#c8e6c9
    style C fill:#fff9c4
    style D fill:#fff9c4
    style E fill:#fff9c4
